{"tid":1831510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[當年今日] 回顧2019年度國際十大新聞，香港竟有兩則上榜","createTime":"2020-01-20T12:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T03:13:31.000Z","uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6fea5a6e3e3c20890a923dac968f8751c9a217","tid":1831510,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"10.<br />\n台北市長柯文哲（前左）16日在西門町紅樓前廣場出席西門町入口意象揭幕儀式，為台北天后宮與台北市政府共同攜手建置的主燈柱揭幕，並與現場民眾握手致意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W558imi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW558imi.jpg&h=5c77922d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.<br />\n台北市長柯文哲（中）28日在台北市孔廟出席107年台北市各界紀念大成至聖先師孔子誕辰2568週年釋奠典禮，在合影時打呵欠。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crbn7er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcrbn7er.jpg&h=cbcf530b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8.<br />\n台北市長柯文哲（右）24日與市府一級主管在三創生活園區，出席「西區翻轉，看見改變<br />\n&mdash;VR360體驗記者會」，柯文哲在台下搔了一下頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4J2Zp1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4J2Zp1F.jpg&h=22e43fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.<br />\n蔡英文總統當地時間20日清晨在丹佛發臉書，強調自己的早餐忍不住泡了一碗泡麵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZq8irr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZq8irr.jpg&h=951a648d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.<br />\n前台北市長朱立倫（中）2日一整天都在高雄活動並且夜宿，3日上午在高雄左營區果貿社區吃早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTCFTVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTCFTVL.jpg&h=a5aa8f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5.<br />\n迎接母親節，參加國民黨總統初選的鴻海董事長郭台銘今（9）日現身內湖花市，期間看到記者鞋帶鬆掉，立即蹲下去幫忙綁鞋帶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t26b0BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft26b0BA.jpg&h=4f540735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n旺角新填地街581號一幢大廈，接近中午發生高空墮物，一個薯仔由高處跌下，擊中一部汽車，車身受損，無人受傷，警方到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜今早到訪高雄果菜市場向民眾派發福袋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6KpBa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6KpBa1.jpg&h=a1de1221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n晚上8時左右，一名36歲男子，在其湖景邨湖碧樓住所露台，發現一個安全套，疑遭人從高處擲下，他只好報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n美國總統川普（Donald Trump) 是日外出吃飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3O5417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3O5417.jpg&h=b593c0cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5452a55a6a9469685e0cb9ddad6504ed68197aa2","tid":1831510,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"轟動世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6147eb9a43261f0713f631b812cf5c84dd8ddad9","tid":1831510,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e928b1f73d3c1855dcb7756ebb764bc6c9e48990","tid":1831510,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:47:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3dce1efde7fb67f5ca22e7f603c8e63f3ed45e","tid":1831510,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaf784daf5a612efa02fb0c10b97c5c863b46f7","tid":1831510,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"第5 做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf73528888f59e6815550a8d8685f45b9ad8757","tid":1831510,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e367484868fb1d7997ad886812d7c29cd7ad503","tid":1831510,"uid":60924,"like":0,"d